There's a note

17:12.069 --> 17:15.038
that the boy
was hospitalized.

17:15.040 --> 17:17.842
Either people
aren't talking

17:17.844 --> 17:21.010
or the right files
didn't survive.

17:21.012 --> 17:24.848
The family's identity
is a mystery.

17:24.851 --> 17:28.751
I can't prove this,

17:28.753 --> 17:32.890
but what if the homeless man

17:32.892 --> 17:36.794
was the boy
on the yacht, grown up?

17:36.796 --> 17:38.562
The Coast Guard report

17:38.564 --> 17:43.633
does match elements
of the homeless man's story.

17:43.635 --> 17:47.071
Could he have slipped through
the cracks over the years,

17:47.073 --> 17:50.908
bouncing from
hospital to hospital,

17:50.910 --> 17:54.010
until all recorded proof

17:54.012 --> 17:57.882
of his existence disappeared?

17:57.884 --> 18:01.684
If the boy grew up

18:01.686 --> 18:03.821
to be the homeless man,

18:03.823 --> 18:07.624
maybe his parents
were the first victims

18:07.626 --> 18:09.796
of whatever it is.

18:11.530 --> 18:12.796
Could the thing in the jug

18:12.798 --> 18:15.632
have something
to do with all this?

18:15.634 --> 18:18.168
She's here now.
She already started.

18:18.170 --> 18:19.636
We know what to do.

18:19.638 --> 18:21.905
Make sure she completes
her task.

18:21.907 --> 18:24.842
We'll make sure that nothing
interferes with this mission.

18:24.844 --> 18:26.680
Everything's depending on it.

18:28.114 --> 18:29.216
Thank you.

18:48.901 --> 18:50.934
So how did your meeting
with Jones go?

18:50.936 --> 18:52.835
You know, he's a suit.

18:52.837 --> 18:54.270
He may be watching this,

18:54.272 --> 18:55.738
you know?

18:55.740 --> 18:57.076
He's a great guy.

18:59.111 --> 19:02.313
You have no idea
who's watching this.

19:02.315 --> 19:03.950
No idea.

19:05.984 --> 19:09.753
Let me tell you something,
Johnson.

19:09.755 --> 19:13.123
I have seen my share
of crazy in my time,

19:13.125 --> 19:16.994
classified shit that would
make your hair turn white.

19:16.996 --> 19:20.064
If the people out there
saw what we saw,

19:20.066 --> 19:21.164
know what we know,

19:21.166 --> 19:24.101
there would be
panic in the streets.

19:24.103 --> 19:27.237
It's what they don't know
that has kept 'em safe.

19:27.239 --> 19:30.173
Think about that.

19:30.175 --> 19:32.875
But this,

19:32.877 --> 19:34.244
this is something else.

19:34.246 --> 19:36.212
This...

19:36.214 --> 19:38.015
this is the big one.

19:38.017 --> 19:42.018
And once Uncle Sam
gets his handle on it,

19:42.020 --> 19:46.055
germ warfare,
special weapons...

19:46.057 --> 19:49.895
they'll never
fuck with us again, ever.

19:51.130 --> 19:52.228
And you and me, Johnson,

19:52.230 --> 19:55.399
we were there
from the beginning...

19:55.401 --> 19:57.737
the day that everything changed.

20:19.290 --> 20:22.692
We are continuously
monitoring the subject.

20:22.694 --> 20:24.827
It is my opinion
that she seems to have a sense

20:24.829 --> 20:26.095
of being watched,

20:26.097 --> 20:28.766
and has developed
some sort of paranoia

20:28.768 --> 20:30.202
of her surroundings.

20:32.771 --> 20:34.203
She seems overwhelmed

20:34.205 --> 20:37.843
showing signs of fatigue
and physical deterioration.

20:40.179 --> 20:42.946
I am unable to deduce
that this could be the reason

20:42.948 --> 20:46.216
Dr. Luiza has been suffering
numerous headaches,

20:46.218 --> 20:50.023
which appears to be escalating
as time passes.

20:52.090 --> 20:55.761
These headaches have become
noticeably more severe.

21:02.034 --> 21:04.034
The others
here at the facility,

21:04.036 --> 21:06.202
they are baffled

21:06.204 --> 21:07.770
and scared.

21:07.772 --> 21:12.476
This epidemic
is reaching everyone

21:12.478 --> 21:17.381
and no one
has a clue, yet.

21:17.383 --> 21:20.249
They are dismissing
my theories.

21:20.251 --> 21:22.419
So what you're suggesting
is that we're dealing

21:22.421 --> 21:25.389
with some giant
prehistoric parasite?

21:25.391 --> 21:26.890
Just look at the video

21:26.892 --> 21:29.759
with the film student.

21:29.761 --> 21:32.863
You can see some kind
of large worm

21:32.865 --> 21:34.965
leap out of the jug.

21:34.967 --> 21:37.133
After that,
he ended up at the beach,

21:37.135 --> 21:38.901
dead, like the others,

21:38.903 --> 21:42.171
like something had forced
its way out of his head.

21:42.173 --> 21:44.040
I don't know what you think
you're seeing in these videos,

21:44.042 --> 21:46.309
'cause there is nothing
conclusive showing any worm

21:46.311 --> 21:47.911
or anything attacking anyone.

21:47.913 --> 21:49.912
There's a black blur.

21:49.914 --> 21:52.349
- That's it.
- Don't you get it?

21:52.351 --> 21:54.785
These worm-like organisms

21:54.787 --> 21:56.754
force their hosts
toward water.

21:56.756 --> 21:58.255
And that's happening

21:58.257 --> 22:00.023
with the victims
in these cases.

22:00.025 --> 22:01.792
They are moving toward water.

22:01.794 --> 22:03.160
If I wanna talk to someone
about parasites,

22:03.162 --> 22:06.196
I have an entire group
dedicated to that field.

22:06.198 --> 22:07.930
But you?

22:07.932 --> 22:09.767
You're supposed to be
working on the brain.

22:09.769 --> 22:11.934
Here's a thought.

22:11.936 --> 22:14.371
Whatever is happening
to these people

22:14.373 --> 22:16.239
is causing brain damage.

22:16.241 --> 22:19.409
So they started doing unexplainable,
irrational things. Simple.

22:19.411 --> 22:22.546
So you need to stop looking
for some bigger conspiracy.

22:22.548 --> 22:27.316
The homeless man,
crazy or not,

22:27.318 --> 22:28.919
may have managed

22:28.921 --> 22:31.157
to bury facts in here.

22:34.826 --> 22:36.093
It could shed some light

22:36.095 --> 22:39.228
on why the student
took the book

22:39.230 --> 22:41.768
then killed himself.

22:43.568 --> 22:46.903
I'll start reading it tonight.

22:46.905 --> 22:49.405
It couldn't hurt.

22:49.407 --> 22:52.176
High command wants
to document our every movement,

22:52.178 --> 22:54.914
so keep glasses on record
at all times.

22:56.015 --> 22:59.449
Copy that.

22:59.451 --> 23:01.921
The subject is leaving
her workplace.

23:11.297 --> 23:12.766
Hey.

23:17.336 --> 23:18.904
Hey!

23:29.048 --> 23:31.116
Do you believe in
a Higher Power?

23:33.352 --> 23:34.617
What're you talking about, man?

23:34.619 --> 23:36.886
Higher Power, man,
Greater Good.

23:36.888 --> 23:40.157
Something bigger than us.

23:40.159 --> 23:41.494
What're you high?

23:42.894 --> 23:44.995
'Cause I could use
a pick me up.

23:44.997 --> 23:46.166
Whatcha got?

23:48.032 --> 23:51.034
- I'm talking about life.
- Life?

23:51.036 --> 23:55.171
Life.
Life with a purpose.

23:55.173 --> 23:56.974
I have a purpose.

23:56.976 --> 23:59.913
Oh yeah,
does it pay money?

24:02.413 --> 24:04.483
The rewards are endless.

24:09.421 --> 24:11.455
Bigger than money.

24:11.457 --> 24:13.159
- Oh, yeah?
- Yeah.

24:19.030 --> 24:21.131
When I was ten,

24:21.133 --> 24:23.033
I thought
my life was over, man,

24:23.035 --> 24:26.303
'cause they,
they took my mom

24:26.305 --> 24:28.173
for a grand mission.

24:29.642 --> 24:31.975
But now I realize it was,
it was an honor, man.

24:31.977 --> 24:35.982
I was chosen to usher in
the dawn a new world order.

24:38.182 --> 24:43.420
Look man, I talk to crazy
dudes all the time,

24:43.422 --> 24:45.488
but you're sick, man.

24:45.490 --> 24:47.924
I know of a free clinic
you can go to.

24:47.926 --> 24:50.163
What if I told you I can
give you anything you want?

24:53.531 --> 24:55.134
A better life.

24:56.602 --> 24:59.937
A better everything.

24:59.939 --> 25:02.639
- I'm listening.
- Yeah?

25:02.641 --> 25:04.274
What if I told you
all you have to do

25:04.276 --> 25:06.512
is look in the water.

25:11.049 --> 25:12.551
Just in there.

25:22.294 --> 25:24.163
Closer.

25:29.268 --> 25:32.035
You see it?

25:32.037 --> 25:33.139
Whoa.

25:36.174 --> 25:37.911
I do see something.

25:40.546 --> 25:43.313
But what is it?

25:43.315 --> 25:45.084
Everything.

25:47.286 --> 25:49.553
Kinda...

25:49.555 --> 25:51.188
Touch it.

25:51.190 --> 25:53.026
Kinda freaky.

26:16.315 --> 26:19.149
I feel.

26:19.151 --> 26:20.586
I serve.

26:22.153 --> 26:24.123
I shall obey.

26:28.760 --> 26:30.393
Thank you so much
for volunteering

26:30.395 --> 26:32.796
for our new world order.

26:32.798 --> 26:36.165
Your time will be
beneficial to you

26:36.167 --> 26:39.135
and to us.

26:39.137 --> 26:40.706
But mostly to us.

26:44.175 --> 26:47.276
I did good, didn't I?

26:47.278 --> 26:49.546
You're on your way?

26:49.548 --> 26:51.183
I'll protect you.

26:54.452 --> 26:57.621
I've been examining this book,

26:57.623 --> 27:00.690
well, if you can
call it a book.

27:00.692 --> 27:03.526
It completely lacks

27:03.528 --> 27:06.496
a coherent narrative.

27:06.498 --> 27:09.498
It makes no sense.

27:09.500 --> 27:12.669
It's just disjointed writing

27:12.671 --> 27:15.705
and crude drawings.

27:15.707 --> 27:19.476
Yet I've spent days,

27:19.478 --> 27:22.379
weeks, going through it.

27:22.381 --> 27:25.082
And there's something there,

27:25.084 --> 27:26.349
something I can't

27:26.351 --> 27:29.186
quite put my finger on.

27:29.188 --> 27:33.556
It's like,
if you weren't careful enough,

27:33.558 --> 27:38.094
just as you were
about to see something,

27:38.096 --> 27:39.830
you'd lose it.

27:39.832 --> 27:41.565
It would be gone

27:41.567 --> 27:44.234
and you'd have to start

27:44.236 --> 27:47.136
all over again.

27:47.138 --> 27:50.306
And that's where
I feel like I am now

27:50.308 --> 27:52.209
squinting at the pages,

27:52.211 --> 27:55.211
on the cusp of something.

27:55.213 --> 27:57.881
Then it's gone.

27:57.883 --> 28:00.784
But there
are some things in here

28:00.786 --> 28:04.821
that seem to tie to it all.

28:04.823 --> 28:06.323
The all of it.

28:06.325 --> 28:09.558
As I examine the pages,

28:09.560 --> 28:11.730
I get this sense of déjà vu.

28:14.432 --> 28:17.767
And when I look
at that image,

28:17.769 --> 28:21.438
it makes me think
of that thing

28:21.440 --> 28:23.142
in the jug.

28:34.819 --> 28:37.187
Okay, Dr. Jones,
ready when you are.

28:37.189 --> 28:39.288
Yes, I'm Dr. Vincent Jones.

28:39.290 --> 28:42.424
It's 10:35 a.m. March 7th,

28:42.426 --> 28:45.497
and I'm here in Autopsy room 3B.

28:46.565 --> 28:49.565
Who are these girls?

28:49.567 --> 28:52.235
Jane Doe's
according to the file.

28:52.237 --> 28:55.238
The poor chicks were fine
24 hours ago.

28:55.240 --> 28:57.340
They were camping together
by the lake.

28:57.342 --> 28:58.607
Who found the bodies?

28:58.609 --> 29:00.610
The local sheriff.

29:00.612 --> 29:03.646
- And where is the sheriff now?
- Not sure.

29:03.648 --> 29:06.516
He disappeared after
the delivery of the bodies.

29:06.518 --> 29:10.286
So what else do you know
what caused this?

29:10.288 --> 29:11.691
Here is the report.

29:16.295 --> 29:17.960
You got anything else?

29:17.962 --> 29:20.697
We took some CT scans
when they were delivered.

29:20.699 --> 29:22.668
The scans are over there.

29:27.506 --> 29:29.842
There's something
in her forehead.

29:38.349 --> 29:40.350
- Dr. Jones?
- What?

29:40.352 --> 29:41.918
- Dr. Jones!
- Help me!

29:41.920 --> 29:44.490
Get the fuck outta here!

29:51.430 --> 29:52.932
Fuck this!

30:06.510 --> 30:08.245
Somebody open the door!

30:08.247 --> 30:09.815
Open the fucking door!

30:12.351 --> 30:13.816
Do we need to contain
this situation?

30:13.818 --> 30:15.619
Yes,

30:15.621 --> 30:19.756
we cannot have this affect or
interfere with our primary target.

30:19.758 --> 30:21.894
Affirmative.
I am on it.

30:38.309 --> 30:39.544
Hey!

30:44.950 --> 30:47.452
Another video came in.

30:49.887 --> 30:51.823
I made sure I got it.

30:56.494 --> 30:59.431
My colleagues
haven't seen it.

31:00.432 --> 31:02.535
They have the bodies...

31:05.671 --> 31:08.975
but I don't know
if they are ready for this.

31:12.443 --> 31:14.311
I'm not sure

31:14.313 --> 31:16.215
any of us are ready.

31:20.085 --> 31:21.851
You're shooting my ass,
aren't you?

31:21.853 --> 31:24.688
Huh? Oh, may be.

31:24.690 --> 31:27.489
- You are such an idiot.
- What? Are you speaking?

31:27.491 --> 31:30.759
I can't really focus
on you right now.

31:30.761 --> 31:34.930
I said that you are going to be
sleeping alone tonight.

31:34.932 --> 31:36.099
Oh, okay, cool.

31:36.101 --> 31:39.469
Keep that up, and I won't
let you do the woman job

31:39.471 --> 31:40.937
of cleaning all the fish.

31:40.939 --> 31:43.840
Hey, we're almost down
by the secret spot there.

31:43.842 --> 31:46.709
Um, I hate to burst your bubble,
Mr. Manly,

31:46.711 --> 31:49.446
but your secret spot
isn't so secret.

31:49.448 --> 31:51.547
What?
Let me see.

31:51.549 --> 31:54.450
My colleagues are focusing

31:54.452 --> 31:55.985
on the bodies,

31:55.987 --> 31:59.855
but not the circumstances
surrounding their condition

31:59.857 --> 32:01.958
and discovery.

32:01.960 --> 32:05.094
I begged them
to look at the book,

32:05.096 --> 32:08.565
at the videos,

32:08.567 --> 32:11.401
and they dismiss me.

32:11.403 --> 32:12.969
But that hasn't stopped me.

32:12.971 --> 32:16.439
Well, what do we have here?
Finders keepers, I guess, huh?

32:16.441 --> 32:18.708
Hey, maybe we should go
somewhere else?

32:18.710 --> 32:21.611
I mean, if that guy comes back and
sees us messing with his stuff

32:21.613 --> 32:23.680
- he might get pissed, you know?
- He's not coming back.

32:23.682 --> 32:25.949
Look. He left his stuff
which is a bit weird

32:25.951 --> 32:27.917
because this rod
is very expensive.

32:27.919 --> 32:30.687
Hey, Ansel Adams, why don't you
come here for a close shot, huh?

32:30.689 --> 32:32.087
Look at this shit.

32:32.089 --> 32:34.657
Maybe he's off in the reeds
going to the bathroom.

32:34.659 --> 32:36.726
- Can we please leave?
- Off in the reeds, babe?

32:36.728 --> 32:39.696
Come on, I mean, look.
His ice is all melted.

32:39.698 --> 32:43.165
- This beer is...
- Oh my God.

32:43.167 --> 32:46.436
It's warm.
He ain't coming back.

32:46.438 --> 32:49.572
Okay, Sherlock, now that
you've used your CSI skills

32:49.574 --> 32:51.106
to give us the time
of death on the beer,

32:51.108 --> 32:54.579
- can we please go?
- All right, come on.

32:58.682 --> 33:00.583
- Come on!
- No, come on, right now.

33:00.585 --> 33:03.585
Let's get outta here, please.
Thank you.

33:03.587 --> 33:06.456
They found the fisherman.

33:06.458 --> 33:09.124
No one
reported him missing,

33:09.126 --> 33:11.428
but work colleagues said

33:11.430 --> 33:14.697
he had taken a week's
vacation to go fishing.

33:14.699 --> 33:17.699
Uh, he was a really good guy.

33:17.701 --> 33:19.102
Uh, very reliable,

33:19.104 --> 33:20.870
fun to hang out with.

33:20.872 --> 33:23.840
You know,
typical everyday guy.

33:23.842 --> 33:26.074
I saw him about
a week-and-a-half ago,

33:26.076 --> 33:28.812
he turned me onto
this great new fishing hole.

33:28.814 --> 33:30.979
Uh, went there,
had a few beers,

33:30.981 --> 33:32.817
you know, normal guy stuff.

33:35.019 --> 33:36.786
This is it.

33:36.788 --> 33:39.491
My new private fishing hole.

33:40.192 --> 33:42.025
Don't let the chain fool you.

33:42.027 --> 33:44.563
It is perfectly legal
to be in here.

33:51.536 --> 33:54.069
I don't know what we're
gonna catch first,

33:54.071 --> 33:57.675
a fish or a buzz, but I guess
it really doesn't matter, right?

34:01.579 --> 34:02.845
This place is great.

34:02.847 --> 34:05.515
I mean,
they just found his body,

34:05.517 --> 34:06.949
his skull was cracked open...

34:06.951 --> 34:08.818
His brains were exposed.

34:08.820 --> 34:10.652
I've never seen anything
quite like that.

34:10.655 --> 34:15.224
Well, why did
he leave his things?

34:15.226 --> 34:17.960
I mean, it's weird. He was like
trying to cook a fish over there.

34:17.963 --> 34:20.728
There was bones and shit but there
was like worms in the fucking ax.

34:20.731 --> 34:22.498
I think we should get
the fuck outta here.

34:22.501 --> 34:24.534
Look.
Someone's coming!

34:24.536 --> 34:25.833
What the fuck
is the matter with this Guy?

34:25.835 --> 34:27.570
Maybe he's hurt,
I don't know.

34:27.572 --> 34:29.137
Hey, buddy,
was that your shit back there?

34:29.139 --> 34:30.572
I'm sorry.
We just didn't...

34:30.574 --> 34:32.809
- Jesus Christ.
- What the fuck?

34:32.811 --> 34:36.547
Stop! Stop!
Stop! What the fuck...

34:48.226 --> 34:51.960
When authorities
discovered his body,

34:51.963 --> 34:55.565
they also discovered
the camera

34:55.567 --> 34:57.233
and the young man.

34:57.235 --> 35:00.135
The young woman
from the video,

35:00.137 --> 35:02.271
she wasn't found at the scene.

35:02.273 --> 35:04.574
She turned up days later.

35:04.576 --> 35:07.142
She tried to steal

35:07.144 --> 35:09.547
someone's tablet computer.

35:14.286 --> 35:16.853
Walked into a coffee shop,

35:16.855 --> 35:20.055
saw the tablet sitting
on a table,

35:20.057 --> 35:21.824
picked it up,

35:21.826 --> 35:24.126
walked out.

35:24.128 --> 35:26.565
Cops caught her
right outside.

35:30.168 --> 35:32.168
She didn't resist.

35:32.170 --> 35:35.304
She didn't say anything.

35:35.306 --> 35:36.940
She still hasn't.

35:36.942 --> 35:40.909
When the authorities found out
she had been flagged,

35:40.911 --> 35:42.744
they brought her here.

35:42.746 --> 35:46.215
They just got done
fighting over the two corpses.

35:46.217 --> 35:49.885
Now there's
a feeding frenzy over her.

35:49.887 --> 35:51.820
But I think
they're wasting their time.

35:51.822 --> 35:56.025
The answers
aren't in the bodies.

35:56.027 --> 35:57.961
They are in the book

35:57.963 --> 36:00.829
and the videos.

36:00.831 --> 36:03.701
And I think
I may have found...

36:06.938 --> 36:08.838
a connection.

36:08.840 --> 36:11.240
We have reports of the phenomena
in every country

36:11.242 --> 36:13.041
with shores
along the Atlantic.

36:13.043 --> 36:14.677
And it's spreading.

36:14.679 --> 36:16.211
We had our first
U.S. case inland.

36:16.213 --> 36:18.046
What happened?

36:18.048 --> 36:20.950
Poor bastard, in a
supermarket in Buffalo

36:20.952 --> 36:22.351
a guy worked
in the seafood section.

36:22.353 --> 36:24.086
He stabbed
his co-worker to death.

36:24.088 --> 36:26.655
He was caught at a bus station
trying to get to a Syracuse.

36:26.657 --> 36:28.023
He offered no resistance,

36:28.025 --> 36:29.825
just like the girl.

36:29.827 --> 36:31.693
If you let me talk to the girl,

36:31.695 --> 36:32.961
I can try to understand

36:32.963 --> 36:35.231
what's happening
to the victims mentally.

36:35.233 --> 36:38.034
I can try to find out what's
compelling them to the beach.

36:38.036 --> 36:40.836
We're moving
the specimen today for tests.

36:40.838 --> 36:43.805
No team member is getting near
her without protective clothing,

36:43.807 --> 36:45.907
because we don't
what we're dealing with.

36:45.909 --> 36:47.644
I know you've
