59:17.059 --> 59:19.394
A teenager.

59:19.396 --> 59:21.396
They never met.

59:21.398 --> 59:25.233
They had no mutual
acquaintances.

59:25.235 --> 59:28.235
They lived near
the Atlantic Ocean,

59:28.237 --> 59:32.606
but hundreds of miles apart.

59:32.608 --> 59:35.744
How is that

59:35.746 --> 59:38.579
they both drew the same thing?

59:38.581 --> 59:41.282
But I don't believe it,

59:41.284 --> 59:43.017
and I don't care anymore.

59:43.019 --> 59:46.220
I don't care.

59:46.222 --> 59:50.090
The nightmares are worse.

59:50.092 --> 59:54.695
Even when I don't sleep,

59:54.697 --> 59:58.402
there isn't any escape.

59:59.702 --> 01:00:01.538
Oh my God!

01:00:22.224 --> 01:00:24.494
I just want to go home.

01:00:29.666 --> 01:00:32.103
I'm going home.

01:00:53.789 --> 01:00:56.490
